request.description:
The Query Projected Billing Report API returns summary report of Projected Billing information through a simple HTTP GET or POST request.

### Data Dictionary

| Field | Type | Description | Required |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `campaignId` | Integer | The numeric id of the campaign | N |
| `cycle1Attrition` | Integer | Percentage of successful rebills for rebill #1 | N (Default is 75) |
| `cycle2Attrition` | Integer | Percentage of successful rebills for rebill #2 | N (Default is 50) |
| `cycle3Attrition` | Integer | Percentage of successful rebills for rebill #3 | N (Default is 50) |
| `cycle4PlusAttrition` | Integer | Percentage of successful rebills for rebill #4+ | N (Default is 50) |
| `endDate` | String (mm/dd/yyyy) | only orders to be billed on or before this date | Y |
| `loginId` | String (max 32 chars) | API Login Id provided by Konnektive | Y |
| `merchantId` | Integer | The numeric id of the gateway | N |
| `password` | String (max 32 chars) | API password provided by Konnektive | Y |
| `recycle1Attrition` | Integer | Percentage of successful bills recycled for attempt #1 | N (Default is 22) |
| `recycle2Attrition` | Integer | Percentage of successful bills recycled for attempt #2 | N (Default is 15) |
| `recycle3Attrition` | Integer | Percentage of successful bills recycled for attempt #3 | N (Default is 7) |
| `recycle4PlusAttrition` | Integer | Percentage of successful bills recycled for attempt #4+ | N (Default is 5) |
| `reportType` | enum (campaign, source, gateway) | Group report by report type | Y |
| `sourceId` | Integer | The numeric id of the source/affiliate | N |
| `startDate` | String (mm/dd/yyyy) | only orders to be billed on or after this date | Y |
| `useActualApprovals` | Boolean ('1' or '0') | Set the Rebill and Recycle Projections based on actual rebills in the last 30 days | N |

